Subject to the terms and conditions of this License, you are
granted a non-exclusive, non-transferable, limited license to
use, copy, and modify DevTrack as follows:

  TIER 1 — PERSONAL (Free)
  ─────────────────────────
  Use by a single individual for personal, non-commercial
  purposes. No seat limit. No payment required. Includes all
  core features and self-hosted deployment.

  TIER 2 — TEAM (Free up to 10 users)
  ─────────────────────────────────────
  Use by an organisation or team of up to ten (10) active
  users. Includes shared workspaces, multi-repo monitoring,
  and all self-hosted features. No payment required.

  TIER 3 — ENTERPRISE (Commercial licence required)
  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Use by an organisation with more than ten (10) active users,
  OR any use in a hosted / SaaS offering provided to third
  parties, requires a separate commercial licence agreement.
  Contact: license@devtrack.dev

